# Patch application order (quilt format).
# One path per line, relative to patches/. Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Applied by tools/apply_patches.py with GNU patch -p1.
#
# Categories:
#   degoogle/  - removal of Google services and background requests
#                (adopted from ungoogled-chromium, Phase 1)
#   privacy/   - T3dmium privacy defaults
#   branding/  - T3dmium name, icons, about page, UA policy
#   features/  - settings UI, first run, adblock, local safe browsing, sync
